column2: Table 2#7B# Wage and Salary Disbursements by Industry, Monthly
[Billions of dollars; months seasonally adjusted at annual rates]
1. Other services-producing industries consists of information; finance and insurance; real
estate and rental and leasing; professional, scientific, and technical services; management
of companies and enterprises; administrative and support and waste management and remediation
services; educational services; health care and social assistance; arts, entertainment, and
recreation; accommodation and food services; and other services.
Note. Estimates in this table are based on the 1997 North American Industry Classification
